Achievements.Name: Bomber
Achievements.Description: Earned by taking out a Nightwalker with a UV mine in Xbox LIVE competition.

Achievements.Name: Savage
Achievements.Description: Earned by scoring 5 kills  in Xbox Live competition without dying once.

Achievements.Name: Berserker
Achievements.Description: Earned by scoring 10 kills in Xbox Live competition without dying once.

Achievements.Name: Rampage
Achievements.Description: Earned by scoring 20 kills in Xbox Live competition without dying once.

Achievements.Name: Kill Frenzy
Achievements.Description: Earned by scoring 3 kills within the 1st min. as a Nightwalker in Xbox Live competition.

Achievements.Name: Despicable One
Achievements.Description: Earned by scoring 20 kills without dying as a Nightwalker in Xbox Live competition.

Achievements.Name: Sniper
Achievements.Description: Earned by scoring a headshot in Xbox Live competition.

Achievements.Name: Stronger
Achievements.Description: Earned by completing a match without dying once in Xbox Live competition.

Achievements.Name: Flame Killer
Achievements.Description: Earned by taking down a Flame carrier.

Achievements.Name: Flame Hero
Achievements.Description: Earned by stealing the opposition's Flame and bringing it back to score.

Achievements.Name: Destroyer
Achievements.Description: Earned by destroying an objective.

Achievements.Name: Dominator
Achievements.Description: Earned by scoring 90 seconds of destruction time.

Achievements.Name: Nightwalker Killer
Achievements.Description: Scored 500 or more Nightwalker kills in single-player mode.

Achievements.Name: Captain
Achievements.Description: Watched the ending sequence in single-player mode.

Achievements.Name: Heavy Gamer
Achievements.Description: Rated "A" or above after clearing all stages in single-player mode.

Achievements.Name: Martial Arts Master
Achievements.Description: Finished off an enemy with a kick in Xbox LIVE competition.

Achievements.Name: All Clear
Achievements.Description: Earned by achieving a Clear Percentage of 100%.

Achievements.Name: Walking Dead
Achievements.Description: Bit 200 times by Nightwalkers.

Achievements.Name: Collector
Achievements.Description: Earned by collecting all medals.

Achievements.Name: Real John Lloyd
Achievements.Description: Cleared all stages in single-player mode at Rank "S".
